 consumer demand in China coupled with</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458070413/image_458070413.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742922-lotus-technology-premium-brand-facing-macro-chaos-and-identity-problem", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 04:48:01"}, {"id": "4742921", "title": "Timing Mutual Fund Sales When Rebalancing A Portfolio", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157187619/image_157187619.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"mutual funds\" data-id=\"157187619\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3100px\" height=\"2067px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157187619/image_157187619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157187619/image_157187619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157187619/image_157187619.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157187619/image_157187619.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157187619/image_157187619.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157187619/image_157187619.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157187619/image_157187619.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157187619/image_157187619.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">blackwaterimages</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I\u2019m keeping this short and sweet.</p> <p>December is traditionally a time when investors review their investments\u2019 performance and rebalance their portfolios. For those who own mutual funds, significant distributions may be forthcoming. Given this, there may be no better time to consider shifting</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157187619/image_157187619.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742921-timing-mutual-fund-sales-when-rebalancing-a-portfolio", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 04:30:23"}, {"id": "4742919", "title": "DIA Vs. DDM: 2 Ways To Play The Dow", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1854380206/image_1854380206.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dow Jones Stock Market Concept with Financial Bar Chart\" data-id=\"1854380206\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1854380206/image_1854380206.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1854380206/image_1854380206.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1854380206/image_1854380206.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1854380206/image_1854380206.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1854380206/image_1854380206.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1854380206/image_1854380206.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1854380206/image_1854380206.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1854380206/image_1854380206.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriori