atic.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1411521203/image_1411521203.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742915-allstate-stock-bull-case-remains-intact-despite-recent-rally", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 02:04:49"}, {"id": "4742914", "title": "QDPL: An Alternative To The 4% Rule For Retirement", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498519579/image_1498519579.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pink piggy bank on a white toy rocket on pink background. Illustration of the concept of skyrocketing stock prices\" data-id=\"1498519579\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498519579/image_1498519579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498519579/image_1498519579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498519579/image_1498519579.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498519579/image_1498519579.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498519579/image_1498519579.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498519579/image_1498519579.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498519579/image_1498519579.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498519579/image_1498519579.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Dragon Claws</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Overview</h2